<i>noun</i>: 요지 [요지], 요령 [요령], 요강 [요강], 개략 [개ː략] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>요지 [요지]</dt><br>
<dd>key points; gist</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 글에서 핵심이 되는 중요한 내용.</dd><br>
<dd>The important parts that are key to a remark or writing.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>요령 [요령]</dt><br>
<dd>1. point; gist; outline</dd><br>
<dd>가장 중요하고 핵심이 되는 줄거리.</dd><br>
<dd>The most important and central plot.</dd><br>
<dd>2. knack; know-how</dd><br>
<dd>경험을 통해 얻은 이치나 방법.</dd><br>
<dd>A principle or method learned through experiences.</dd><br>
<dd>3. trick</dd><br>
<dd>적당히 해 넘기려는 얕은 꾀.</dd><br>
<dd>A shallow trick for doing something carelessly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>요강 [요강]</dt><br>
<dd>main point; main thrust; gist</dd><br>
<dd>기본이 되는 줄거리나 중심이 되는 내용.</dd><br>
<dd>A summary of main points or thread of a story.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>개략 [개ː략]</dt><br>
<dd>outline; summary; gist</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 사건의 내용을 짧게 줄임.</dd><br>
<dd>An abbreviated version of a certain incident or case.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>